message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As a paralegal and legal assistant, my role involves preparing, editing, and reviewing a variety of legal documents. This includes drafting legislation, creating and refining legal briefs, preparing pleadings for court, assisting in the preparation of appeals, drafting wills, reviewing and drafting contracts, and preparing real estate closing statements. Each document requires careful attention to detail, ensuring compliance with legal standards and accuracy in content to support legal proceedings and transactions effectively.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
